reviewText: COUGAR MOTHER & 2 KITTENS WILDLIFE DOCUMENTARY-In this tale of discovery you watch the birth of 2 cougar kittens in the high country of Utah. See how the mother protects and teaches her playful, adventurous kittens. Watch them grow and learn to hunt. Witness their encounters with a bull snake and a tortoise. With captivating wildlife scenes Curious Cougar Kittens is a wonderful addition to your Mother Nature Tales Of Discovery video collection or a great gift for a loved one who enjoy's Nature & it's wonders!
